<br>
If you declare a residence, it seems you can summon pets anywhere.  Tent or no tent.  Even on the run.<br>
<br>
I threw up a house on Corellia, and declared it my residence.  Now, running to and from places on Dath, Dantooine, Endor, etc., I can store and call pets as I go.  No tents, no outposts, no nothin'.  Call on the run.<br>
